{
  "name": "Ignite Health Systems - Monthly Content Pipeline",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "0 9 1 * *"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "cron_trigger",
      "name": "Monthly Trigger (1st at 9am)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [250, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "modelId": {
          "mode": "list",
          "value": "gemini-1.5-flash"
        },
        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "You are an AI healthcare expert writing for Ignite Health Systems. Research and analyze the latest healthcare AI developments from the past 30 days.\n\nFocus on:\n1. Breakthrough AI technologies in healthcare\n2. Clinical AI implementations\n3. FDA approvals and regulatory updates\n4. Major funding rounds and partnerships\n\nAnalyze through these lenses:\n- Extractive vs Regenerative (does it empower physicians or replace them?)\n- Enhancement vs Replacement (cognitive extension or automation?)\n- Net-Positive Outcomes (reducing harm and burnout)\n\nProvide a comprehensive research summary with specific examples and data points.",
              "role": "user"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "temperature": 0.3,
          "maxTokens": 2048
        }
      },
      "id": "gemini_research",
      "name": "Gemini - Research Phase",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatGoogleGemini",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [450, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "modelId": {
          "mode": "list",
          "value": "gemini-1.5-flash"
        },
        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "Based on this research:\n\n{{ $json.text }}\n\nWrite a compelling 750-word article for the Ignite Health Systems newsletter.\n\nRequirements:\n- Address the transition from document-centric healthcare to AI-native future\n- Use our key terminology: 'Platform Fragmentation Crisis', 'unified clinical co-pilot'\n- Contrast extractive vs regenerative AI approaches\n- Write in Dr. Murji's voice: authoritative, mission-driven, empathetic\n- Include specific examples from the research\n- End with a call to action for joining the Innovation Council\n\nTone: Professional yet accessible, urgency without fear-mongering, hope grounded in reality.",
              "role": "user"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "temperature": 0.4,
          "maxTokens": 2048
        }
      },
      "id": "gemini_article",
      "name": "Gemini - Article Generation",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatGoogleGemini",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [650, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "append",
        "documentId": {
          "mode": "list",
          "value": "1kPYgthwKzREJYKjAnE4h1YFMRxg5ulynrbDYNRxb8Lo"
